      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system in peak operational state. This manual-equipped example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and documented rod bearing replacement, mitigating common platform weak points. The M-Variable limited-slip differential provides surgical power delivery, while the factory suspension maintains perfect damping characteristics and bushing integrity. The exterior retains its original deep luster with no evidence of oxidation or panel misalignment, complemented by a cockpit with zero bolster wear. A mechanically synchronized, collector-grade specimen.",
